&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jun 2011 15:44:15 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl12/free-culture</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl12/free-culture</guid></item><item><title>Sambacidade: heating up for fisl12 and the 5th City Congress</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="/articles/0032/8484/brasil03-800x523-.jpg1307380257" height="161" alt="Brasil03__800x523_" style="float: left; margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 3px; margin-left: 6px; margin-right: 6px;" width="248"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;Sambacidade is a group of popularisation events for the 12th International Free Software Forum and the 5th City Congress. They will happen during June, in Porto Alegre, organized by the Free Software Association (ASL), in partnership with the Innovation and Technology Office (Inovapoa) and the Governance Department.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Four cultural activities are planned throughout the city. the progamme includes presentations of the Brasilidades Institute and of cultural production groups that relate to free culture, such as Rabo de Arraia, Africanamente, Malta dos Guris e das Gurias de Rua, among others. There will also be shows of videos and debates about free culture, with ASL representatives, of the cultural groups and the offices and departments. The events are free and open to the whole of the Porto Alegre city community.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Check out the dates and venues:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;June, 17 – IFRS - Campus Restinga- Starting at 7 PM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;June, 18&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt; – Instituto Cultural Afrosul - Odomodê- &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;Starting at 3 PM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;June, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;25 – Praça Alexandre Zachia- &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;Starting at 10 AM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;June, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;26 – Usina do Gasômetro- &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;Starting at 2 PM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;12th International Free software Forum&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;The International Free Software Forum happens every year in the city of Porto Alegre, RS, Brazil. Considere done of the largest events in the world for promoting technical, political and social thinking about free software in an integrated way, fisl gathers debates, speeches, personalities and novelties both national and international, in the world of free software and culture. The 12th edition of the International Free Software Forum will happen from June, 29 to July, 2, 2011 in the PUCRS Center of Events.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5th City Congress&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;The 5th City Congress, in Porto Alegre, proposes to reafirm the path to democratization of Porto Alegre, by gathering movements that make the city an international reference in its democratic processes. It is an opportunity to integrate efforts for a better future, and a city for all citizens. Where human and material assets work together, in search of concrete actions and may then keep this integration permanently.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jun 2011 14:46:42 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl12/fisl12/noticias/sambacidade-heating-up-for-fisl12-and-the-5th-city-congress</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl12/fisl12/noticias/sambacidade-heating-up-for-fisl12-and-the-5th-city-congress</guid></item><item><title>fisl12 to have pre-launch with soiree</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;img src="/articles/0032/1760/cultura3.jpg1305641814" height="155" alt="cultura3" style="float: left; margin-top: 3px; margin-bottom: 3px; margin-left: 6px; margin-right: 6px;" width="235"&gt;With live music from Porto Alegre musicians committed to the free culture and technology movements, fisl12 - International Free Software Forum - will have a pre-launch in May, 20, at Entreato Bar, Porto alegre, RS.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;The soiree will have Richard Serraria, musician from the MPB (movement lead by musicians and free culture activists, devoted to creating room for discussions about music, technology and colaborative communication) and Instituto &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;Brasilidades&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt; (cultural institute created to foster popular brazilian culture in Rio Grande do Sul state). There will be also  a photographic exhibition and audio/video projections about that subject, such as "A Guerrilha Midiática" ("Media Guerrilas") from Coletivo Catarse (group of communicators devoted to building alternatives to strengthen culture and independent journalism).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;fisl promotes the Free Culture Festival, every edition, that happens during the event, aimed at gathering together hackers, artists, developers and cultural producers, fostering free software as a basis for free culture. During fisl12, there will be workshops, speeches, art performances and night parties.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;The fisl12 pre-launch soiree starts as 8PM, at Entreato Bar, Rua da República, 163. Entry fee is R$ 10.00.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;fisl12 happens from June, 29, to July, 2 at the Center of Events, PUCRS, Porto Alegre, RS, Brazil.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 May 2011 12:11:01 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl12/fisl12/noticias/fisl12-to-have-pre-launch-with-soiree</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl12/fisl12/noticias/fisl12-to-have-pre-launch-with-soiree</guid></item></channel></rss>